data.description: Welcome home! Located in the highly desirable gated community of The Highlands this MOVE IN READY home, just under 2,000 Sq.feet, offers 4 bedrooms 2 bathrooms, a study, 2 car garage, and spacious backyard . This gorgeous home also offers many upgrades including vinyl flooring, fully fenced in yard, accent wall, high ceilings, along with a new roof (2021), garage door (2021) and A/C (2019).  Making this home yours allows you access to the wonderfully kept community pool and your monthly dues cover your cable, WiFi, trash, lawn care, irrigation, pest control, and maintenance of common areas. The community of The Highlands is just a quick drive to everything you could need; grocery stores, shopping, restaurants, beaches and more.  Come tour your future home today!
